OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FThe leader of the Conservatives has
OL,8,Fvowed her party wouldn't do deals with
OL,9,Fanyone "not delivering", after May's
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FKemi Badenoch told ITV News, "the only
OL,13,Fdeal we're doing is a deal with the
OL,14,FWelsh people", adding the Welsh
OL,15,FConservatives "have got a plan for
OL,16,FWales".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
