OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FAlthough, when pressed on which party
OL,8,Fthey would work with, she said "We
OL,9,Fwould work with people who want to cut
OL,10,Fa penny off income tax, we would work
OL,11,Fwith people who want to scrap the
OL,12,Fstamp duty. Those are our policies.
OL,13,FPeople who want to cap council tax",
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"Any party that has ideas like that,
OL,17,Fwe'll help them with votes and so on.
OL,18,FBut deals where we will allow a party
OL,19,Fjust to be in government but not
OL,20,Fdelivering? Absolutely not."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
