OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FAccording to an ITV Cymru Wales poll,
OL,8,Fthe Conservatives are behind in the
OL,9,Fpolls at 8%. The poll also projects
OL,10,Fthat the Conservative leader, Darren
OL,11,FMillar, would lose his seat.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Conservatives are the only
OL,14,Fparty not to rule out working with
OL,15,FReform UK, who are currently projected
OL,16,Fto win 29%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
