OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FMr Millar told ITV News, "people are
OL,8,Funderstanding that in order to get rid
OL,9,Fof Labour, they need to make sure that
OL,10,Fthey think carefully about where to
OL,11,Fput vote".
OL,13,FVisiting Pembroke Dock on Thursday,
OL,14,FKemi Badenoch also admitted her party
OL,15,Fhad been damaged by the 2024 general
OL,16,Felection result.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
