OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FShe said, "I think that the election
OL,8,Fwe had in 2024 showed that the
OL,9,Fnational party had lost the trust of
OL,10,Fthe public, and it takes time to win
OL,11,Ftrust back.
OL,13,F"We've got a new Conservative Party
OL,14,Fwith new leadership. Darren Millar is
OL,15,Fnew leadership here in Wales. We are
OL,16,Fdoing things differently. We have
OL,17,Flearned from the mistakes of the past.
OL,19,F"We acknowledge what went wrong, and
OL,20,Fnow we are changing to fix them", said
OL,21,FMs Badenoch.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
