OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FThe Welsh Conservatives have pledged
OL,8,Fto cut the basic rate of income tax by
OL,9,F1p and scrap stamp duty in Wales if
OL,10,Fthey are elected in May's Senedd
OL,11,Felection.
OL,13,FThey've also pledged caps on council
OL,14,Ftax increases, delivering an M4 relief
OL,15,Froad and reversing the increase in the
OL,16,Fnumber of Members of the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
