OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives won't do deals
OL,4,Cwith parties that won't deliver -
OL,5,CBadenoch
OL,7,FKemi Badenoch said, "The Conservatives
OL,8,Fhave a plan to take a penny off income
OL,9,Ftax, they want to scrap stamp duty,
OL,10,Fthey want to cut some taxes. These are
OL,11,Fgreat policies that will help fix
OL,12,FWales.
OL,14,F"They've got a plan for the NHS here,
OL,15,Fdeclaring an emergency, and more beds.
OL,16,FThey are thinking about what the
OL,17,Freport's problems are, and how to fix
OL,18,Fthem."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
